data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!! Turn Key Ready!! This home is ready for you to move-on-in. This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home was designed with you in mind, offering the perfect blend of contemporary design and functional living. With an open floor plan, this residence is an inviting canvas for your personal touch, where every detail has been carefully crafted to ensure comfort and style. The open concept leaves plenty of room for entertaining, seamlessly connecting the living room, dining area, and kitchen for effortless entertaining and family gatherings. Relax and rejuvenate in the expansive master suite, complete with a walk-in closet and a spa-like ensuite bathroom. Say goodbye to clutter with several closets and storage areas throughout the home, including a generous walk-in pantry in the kitchen. The split floorplan provides ultimate privacy, with the master suite separate from the secondary bedrooms. Step outside to your back patio and spacious yard, perfect for outdoor dining, play, or simply unwinding in the fresh air. Enjoy mature landscaping that adds both beauty and shade to your backyard oasis. Embrace the tranquility of living near lakes and parks, making it easy to enjoy outdoor adventures and scenic views. This home's prime location offers proximity to shopping centers, major roads, and all the conveniences of modern living. This is not just a house; it's a lifestyle waiting for you to embrace. Your dream home is just a call away! Includes a brand-new washer/dryer and security system!
